## ADIM 2 — SOLUTION VE PROJE OLUŞTURMA

### 2.1 Solution oluştur
```bash
dotnet new sln -n Traxon.CryptoTrader
```

### 2.2 `src/` projeleri oluştur
```bash
# Domain (classlib)
dotnet new classlib -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Domain -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Domain

# Application (classlib)
dotnet new classlib -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Application -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Application

# Infrastructure (classlib)
dotnet new classlib -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Infrastructure -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Infrastructure

# Binance adapter (classlib)
dotnet new classlib -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Binance -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Binance

# Polymarket adapter (classlib - FAZ 1'DE BOŞ, sadece proje iskeleti)
dotnet new classlib -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Polymarket -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Polymarket

# Worker (worker service)
dotnet new worker -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Worker -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Worker

# Dashboard (blazor server - FAZ 1'DE BOŞ ISKELET)
dotnet new blazorserver -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Dashboard -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Dashboard

# Admin (blazor server - FAZ 1'DE BOŞ ISKELET)
dotnet new blazorserver -n Traxon.CryptoTrader.Admin -o src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Admin
```

